videos.description: USC outlasted Stanford in the Pac-12 championship as the Trojans took down the Cardinal 31-28. Sam Darnold threw for 325 yards and 2 touchdowns in the Trojans first Pac-12 championship victory since 2008.
videos.title: College Football: USC beats Stanford in the Pac-12 Championship

location: Bobby Bowden Field at Doak Campbell Stadium, Tallahassee, FL
Aggie Memorial Stadium, Las Cruces, NM

videos.description: Ohio State scored a bunch early and held off a comeback against Wisconsin to win the Big Ten Championship 27-21. J. K. Dobbins ran for 174 yards for the Buckeyes, while J. T. Barrett had two passing touchdowns and one rushing touchdown.
videos.title: College Football: Ohio State holds off Wisconsin for Big Ten Title

location: Bank of America Stadium, Charlotte, NC
